data.description: Discover the allure of this 5-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom residence featuring a spacious 3-car garage. Set amidst the picturesque mountains of the Hampton Cove area, this home immerses you in natural beauty and serenity. Enjoy the charm of a delightful neighborhood boasting a clubhouse, pool, and proximity to excellent Huntsville city schools. Step inside to experience the inviting ambiance of open and well-lit rooms adorned with soaring ceilings, gleaming hardwood floors, and luxurious Cambria Quartz (Harrogate) countertops. The expansive layout includes a Family Room, Study, formal Dining Room, Breakfast area, and a generously sized Rec Room complete with a wet bar, wine cooler, and a balcony.
